<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>The Young Right</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      color: #7a0000;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .menu, .cart {
      font-size: 24px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .hero {
      margin: 20px auto;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 900px;
      background: #fff;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }

    .hero-text {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .hero-text h2 {
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: normal;
    }

    .hero-text h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .sub-text {
      margin: 15px auto;
      width: 80%;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #7a0000;
    }

    .gallery {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      background: #a00000;
    }

    .gallery img {
      width: 30%;
      min-width: 120px;
      height: auto;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #555;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <header>
    <div class="menu">☰</div>
    <div class="logo">
      THE<br>YOUNG<br>RIGHT
    </div>
    <div class="cart">🛒 0</div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <img src="your-image.jpg" alt="Beach Image">

    <div class="hero-text">
      <h2>THE YOUNG RIGHT</h2>
      <h1>The fastest-growing Conservative Lifestyle Brand in America.</h1>
      <h2><em>Entirely led and run by Gen Z.</em></h2>

      <div class="section-title">
        EDITORIAL PODCAST EVENTS<br>
        ACTIVATIONS MERCH AMBASSADORS
      </div>

      <div class="sub-text">
        We understand how to reach, influence, and impact the next generation
        because we are the next generation.<br><br>
        <em>And, it’s working.</em>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="gallery">
    <img src="img1.jpg" alt="">
    <img src="img2.jpg" alt="">
    <img src="img3.jpg" alt="">
  </section>

  <footer>
    © 2026 The Young Right
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
